node.text:
I love my city! Leaving Chicago will be bittersweet for me. I want to thank each of y’all for coming and pushing through til the end! We had expectant mothers, kids, Men, & women of all ages, shapes, and sizes! 

I swear I will never get used to this! I am so grateful for each and every single one of you! 

NYC 📍 ATL 📍HOUSTON📍

Y’all got next! 😈 START HYDRATING NOWWWWWWWWWWWW

🎥: @ricer90 ☄️🔥💫

node.text:
Soooo I lost between 2 & 3 inches on my waist in 5 days! 🥲 shoutout to Dr.Kim! 🙌🏾 @kim_keepitmoving for setting me up on her cleanse! Had to hop on live with her & talk about my personal experience. While she filled me all the way in on all the wonderful benefits. 

If you’re interest in trying the detox Click the link in her bio, but don’t forget to dm her & tell her I sent you for a gift with your purchase. ☺️

node.text:
Bend & Snap NYC 

“Y’all are gonna hate me in about 15minutes” 🤣🤣 that part is important! 

Still high from this trip! 😍 NYC never disappoints. The energy was everything! 

Thank you to everyone who has been a part of this tour! Online & in person. Thank y’all so much for allowing me to push you pass your limits. & then some! Lol. You know I do it all out of love! 🤎 & I am so grateful To have all of that love returned to me 🥰

Always blissful ✨

Bend & Snap Online flexibility & strength training

We’re getting BACK TO THE BASICS 😃 This class will be beginner BEGINNER friendly! But can also be very beneficial to anyone further into their practice!
We will be touching on form & technique to improve flexibility! 

For all of my first timers who have been too afraid to try my classes 👀 This ones for you! I promise to get as close to gentle as I can! 😅

To sign up, link in bio ✨

📸: @interscopephotography 💫 ✨

node.text:
I love my city! Leaving Chicago will be bittersweet for me. I want to thank each of y’all for coming and pushing through til the end! We had expectant mothers, kids, Men, & women of all ages, shapes, and sizes! 

I swear I will never get used to this! I am so grateful for each and every single one of you! 

NYC 📍 ATL 📍HOUSTON📍

Y’all got next! 😈 START HYDRATING NOWWWWWWWWWWWW

🎥: @ricer90 ☄️🔥💫
